<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.3.5">
<l>tammaiyē nāḷum vaṇaṅkit toḻuvārkku</l>
<l>tammaiyē yokka varuḷceyva rātalāl</l>
<l>tammaiyē nāḷum vaṇaṅkit toḻutiṟaiñci</l>
<l>tammaiyē paṟṟā maṉatteṉṟum vaittōmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To us who worship, adoring him daily,</l>
<l>He gives grace which befits him; therefore,</l>
<l>Worshiping, bowing low, adoring him daily,</l>
<l>While clinging to him, we keep him always in [our] minds.</l> 
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
